snippet.title: Mikhaila Peterson
snippet.description:
I use the Mikhaila Peterson Podcast as a chance to talk to thought leaders, influencers and industry changers. I'm speaking with everyone from CEO's to fitness enthusiasts to spiritual guides, nutrition researchers to health professionals. These episodes are interview-style conversations aimed at provoking thought, addressing difficult subjects, and delving into topics that are generally shied away from.
